  "instructions": [
    "In a large bowl, combine the baby lettuce leaves, Kalamata olives, artichoke hearts, and grilled halloumi cheese.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the extra virgin olive oil, lemon juice, garlic, dried oregano, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Pour the dressing over the salad and toss to combine.",
    "Sprinkle the roasted red peppers and chopped parsley over the top of the salad.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste."
